Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:45.58,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:52.77,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Mimpi rupanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.77,0:22:57.02,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Tak syak lagi, aku masih tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:03.44,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Kenapa aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.95,0:23:06.16,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,tidur dengan perempuan telanjang?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.72,0:23:19.12,Sara,Sara,0,0,0,,K-Kenapa ni, Rio-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.09,0:23:24.53,Orfia,Orfia,0,0,0,,Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.53,0:23:25.66,Alma,Alma,0,0,0,,Kenapa? Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.66,0:23:27.13,Latifa,Latifa,0,0,0,,Apa ni?
